{"tid":730421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滬女海航大廈外向習畫像潑墨","createTime":"2018-07-05T11:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T02:38:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2c73d791316b2f047c121ee3c309203fef8fa277","tid":730421,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:37:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180705/20440784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F20440784&d=wz%2FZjKwIRaCioXb8dQfv8cPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=c20cb849\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F20440784&h=af87e1a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180705/20440784</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月05日 <br />\n<br />\n滬女海航大廈外向習畫像潑墨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180705/large/a0405a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180705%2Flarge%2Fa0405a.gif&h=18c12c51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■上海一名女子昨早直播在海航大廈前向習畫像潑墨。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】海航集團是非纏身，上海一名女子宣稱為反對總書記習近平獨裁專制，昨早在上海海航大廈前將墨水潑向路邊的習近平畫像洩憤，事件震驚內地社會，她被網民封為「潑墨女孩」。女子在Twitter的最後留言指「門外有一群制服的人」，其後網上所有留言被刪、賬號顯示為不存在，目前未知下落。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳的影片顯示，昨晨6時40分，網名feefeefly的女子身穿印有New York字樣的黃色T恤，在位於陸家嘴的海航大廈前宣稱以實名制反對習近平獨裁專制、暴政，並反對中共對她實施腦控壓迫。<br />\n<br />\n她在影片中高呼：「我反對，我對他恨之入骨。」隨後手執墨水，潑向路邊宣傳畫上的習近平，指要在屬習資產的海航大廈前面潑墨，過程在網上直播。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發文稱門外有制服人員後失蹤<br />\n<br />\n潑墨影片在Twitter中文圈引起譁然，不少網民擔心其安危，要她好好保護自己。直至昨午3時許，feefeefly再次在Twitter發文：「現在我的門外有一群制服的人。待會換好衣服就出去。我沒有罪。有罪的是傷害我的人和組織。」內地異見藝術家華湧建議她不要開門出去，用手機轉播經過。然而她的Twitter此後再沒更新，過去的發文也全被刪，隨後連賬戶亦顯示為不存在，未知是被封鎖或自行刪除。<br />\n<br />\n網上消息指，潑墨女孩叫董瑤瓊，在好租科技上海分公司工作，據說是湖南株洲人。有指她自稱受腦控迫害，被當成政治博弈傳聲筒，因討厭中共獨裁專制而在網上發聲，導致失業、失戀，曾想自殺。《蘋果》記者嘗試致電網傳董的電話，但無法打通。網民將潑墨女孩與天安門毛澤東畫像潑墨案相提並論，1989年5月，被稱天安門三勇士的喻東嶽、余志堅和魯德成，將沾滿顏料的雞蛋擲向天安門城樓的毛澤東畫像，3人被判重刑。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n遊客身份寄居3年　洋同志一家終安心<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n澳門食店意外1死3重傷　石油氣大爆炸活埋孝順女"},{"pid":"b2156359b7e284768095fc2c1bdcfd12e4c51780","tid":730421,"uid":79145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"大獲了，習總份人⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c9182f88b3915419da7151ac54f75708fb69d7","tid":730421,"uid":155177,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:03:34.000Z","msg":"覺醒支那人<br />\n<br />\n幫佢BACKUP先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/200222_c2601f15667ab44668130f52546b4186.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F200222_c2601f15667ab44668130f52546b4186.png&h=05c6835d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/200222_51ec2e09b4d4cd4a7cb05b01f6d86cfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F200222_51ec2e09b4d4cd4a7cb05b01f6d86cfa.jpg&h=ff7332d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/200222_b60d9d39966d955833e5c2084779e9e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F200222_b60d9d39966d955833e5c2084779e9e8.jpg&h=e03fcab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/200223_4ce7e6616b299ea3826f041d2cf39362.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F200223_4ce7e6616b299ea3826f041d2cf39362.jpg&h=6d606c31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/200223_c7a718ed1f1a7e12465c7899a7b3f7e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2F